---
import P1 from "../images/primary/p1.jpg"
import P2 from "../images/primary/p2.jpg"
import P3 from "../images/primary/p3.jpg"
import './primary.css'
import Book from "../images/kinder/Book.png"
import Kindercard from "../kindergarten/kindercard.astro"
---

<section  class="primary">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="title text-center pb-5">
        <span class="orange">Nurturing  young minds, fostering academic growth</span>, and <span class="orange">shaping </span> well-rounded individuals for a successful educational journey.
      </p>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-3">
            <img src="/primary/p1.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-3">
            <img src="/primary/p2.jpg" alt="">

        </div>
        <div class="col-3">
            <img src="/primary/p3.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="title mt-5 pt-5 pb-5 text-center">
        Our <span>Primary School</span> Highlights
      </div>

      <p class="text-center   pb-5">
        primary classes serve as a foundational and formative stage in a child's education, providing a structured and supportive environment where students begin to develop essential skills, knowledge, and a love for learning that will shape their educational journey.
      </p>

     <div class="course-contents">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <Kindercard  title="Comprehensive Curriculum"  words=" Primary school offers a comprehensive curriculum that encompasses core subjects such as English, mathematics, science, and social studies. It also includes additional subjects like art, music, physical education, and foreign languages, providing a well-rounded education." image={Book}  />
        </li>
        <li>
          <Kindercard  title="Academic Development"  words=" Primary school focuses on advancing academic skills and knowledge. Students develop strong reading and writing abilities, critical thinking skills, problem-solving strategies, and mathematical reasoning. They explore scientific concepts, historical events, and cultural understanding through engaging lessons and hands-on activities." image={Book}  />
        </li>
        <li>
          <Kindercard  title="Individualized Learning"  words=" Primary school recognizes the diverse learning needs of students. Teachers provide differentiated instruction, adapting teaching methods and materials to accommodate varying abilities and learning styles. This approach ensures that each student receives the support they need to succeed." image={Book}  />
        </li>
        <li>
          <Kindercard  title="Social and Emotional Growth"  words=" Primary school promotes the development of social and emotional skills. Students learn to collaborate, communicate effectively, and work in teams. They develop empathy, respect for others, and understanding of diverse perspectives. Character education programs foster values such as honesty, kindness, and responsibility." image={Book}  />
        </li>
        <li>
          <Kindercard  title="Co-Curricular Activities"  words=" Primary school offers a range of co-curricular activities, including sports, clubs, and extracurricular programs. These activities provide opportunities for students to explore their interests, develop new talents, and foster teamwork and leadership skills outside the classroom." image={Book}  />
        </li>
      </ul>

      
     </div>
     <p class="text-center pt-5">
      Primary school is an exciting and transformative time where students continue to grow academically, socially, and emotionally. It prepares them for the challenges and opportunities that lie ahead in their educational journey, laying a strong foundation for future success.
    </p>
    </div>
</section>